description: The video shows an animated image of a woman with blonde, wavy hair, red lipstick, and fair skin against a white background. She is wearing a magenta low-cut top and a purple blazer. Initially, she is looking down and filing her nails. At the second mark, her eyes open, revealing blue irises, and she lifts her gaze to the upper left, as if noticing us. She makes an annoyed expression and continues to hold the nail file in her hand.
